data.text:
Mark Woodforde - Doubles Legend

17 times Grand Slam Champion, and doubles legend Mark Woodforde joins us for a chat. One half of the iconic 'Woodies' partnership, as well US Open Champ with none other than John McEnroe.

Mark talks honestly about his career, learning from McEnroe, how singles players should play doubles and loads more.

Join us for the best episode yet!

Subscribe and share.

The Tennis Podcast of choice. Join Keith Fraser & former British number 1 and Davis Cup Captain John Lloyd on the entertaining, relaxed and fun tennis show. Tennis, but not only tennis. as this show looks at interesting and fun topics in the sport as well as guests from the tennis & sporting world, politics, business & showbiz. Rock n' Roll Tennis is your home for your tennis fix. Be sure to Subscribe, Share & Review.
